---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
  <main>
    <div class="welcome">
      <h1 class="title">Welcome to FrankÂ´s world!</h1>
      <span class="description">
        Discover the secrets of trading with Frank, the expert in trading robots
        based on Smart Money. <br /> With years of experience in the financial markets,
        Frank has developed a series of products and services <br /> designed to
        take your trading to the next level. From highly efficient trading robots
